Terrace Bank of Florida said it is selling500,000 shares of stock at 10.50 dlrs per share in its initialoffering.    The organizers of the bank plan to purchase 81,000 of thoseshares, which will have a par value of five dlrs.    Individual investors may purchase as few as 100 shares ofthe stock, the bank said. The offering is slated to end by May15, but could be extended, it said. Reuter&#3;